=== run example

  gluon_example -d example
  cd example
  rake

see http://localhost:9292 for default.

=== run example at deployment mode

  gluon_example -d example
  cd example
  rake server_deploy

see http://localhost:9292 for default.

=== run example with project local rubygems repository

  gluon_example -d example
  cd example
  rake local_gem "GEM_ARGS=install gluon"
  rake local_server

see http://localhost:9292 for default.<br>
see <tt>example/gems</tt> for local rubygems repository.

=== run example CGI

  gluon_example -d example
  cd example
  rake local_gem "GEM_ARGS=install gluon"
  rake local_cgi_env
  rake cgi_server

see http://localhost:9292/gluon.cgi for default.
